%% Data Science Pipelines - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant IstioGW as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MLUI as ml-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ml-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant S3 as MinIO / S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ArgoCtrl as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Driver as kfp-driver<br/>(init container)
    participant Launcher as kfp-launcher<br/>(container)
    participant Cache as cache-server<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant PA as ml-pipeline-persistenceagent
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant MW as metadata-writer

    Note over User,MW: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution
    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>Auth: username/password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>Auth: Access Key
    API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>ArgoCtrl: Watch event (new Workflow)
    ArgoCtrl->>Driver: Execute init container
    Driver->>Launcher: Hand off to launcher

    Note over User,MW: Flow 2: Cache Check (Mutating Webhook)
    K8s->>Cache: Pod creation webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    Cache->>DB: Check cache entry<br/>Auth: username/password
    Cache-->>K8s: Mutate pod (cached/uncached)

    Note over User,MW: Flow 3: Persistence Agent Sync
    PA->>K8s: Watch Argo Workflows<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status updates
    PA->>API: Report run status<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: SA Token

    Note over User,MW: Flow 4: Metadata Tracking
    MW->>MLMD: Write execution metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC plaintext

    Note over User,MW: Flow 5: UI Access (Multi-User Mode)
    User->>IstioGW: HTTPS Request<br/>Auth: Session/OAuth
    IstioGW->>MLUI: HTTP 80/TCP<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>kubeflow-userid header
    MLUI->>API: Proxy API call<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API-->>MLUI: JSON Response
    MLUI-->>IstioGW: HTML/JSON Response
    IstioGW-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,MW: Flow 6: Scheduled/Recurring Run
    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>Auth: SA Token
    Note right of K8s: ml-pipeline-scheduledworkflow<br/>watches ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>creates Argo Workflows on schedule
